            </a>
            <a class="sns-icon be" title="behance" href="https://www.behance.net/codeui">
                <i class="icon2 icon-be"></i>
            </a>
            <p class="quote">You Can Speak <strong>"Hi"</strong> to Me in Those Ways</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>



